<br />
Scholte, E.J., Ng'habi, K., Kihonda, J., Takken, W., Paaijmans, K., Abdulla, S., Killeen, G. F. and Knols, B. G. J. 2005. An entomopathogenic fungus for control of adult African malaria mosquitoes. Science 308: 1641-1642.<br />
<br />
